You have to play for first Liu

This is the second example today about necessity of the four.

The following moves are a bit peculiar, but I cannot find any other way.
The idea of the 23rd move is to connect the upper side win with lower side one.
Now the 23rd stone works in both horizontal and vertical line.
Move 26 - the only one that blocks both wins.
